channel.title: Error, im sure mopar can help me
channel.description:
Well, i've been trying to get my friend on a downloaded silabs client, when something similar to this popped up
http://s153.photobucket.com/albums/s217/raberboy23/?action=view&current=gayness.jpg
I've done everything my hands possible. I've walked him through on making sure his computer recognizes java and everything. He has the newest jre and jdk update. But yet for some odd reason, he still gets this error. He has also cleared his browser cache on both IE and Mozzilla. Any suggestions to what he should do next? Dont spam this thread, i need useful information please. Also this happens after he unpacks configurations in silabs.
Note: none of this happens in the regular moparscape client when he runs it.
